From 74cdcf45a759b2285f49845e58bf30c7ffb9ca52 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jan Martens <44572196+JanMa@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Thu, 26 Mar 2026 12:27:20 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 19/22] Address Ember-Data array like deprecation (#2705)

* fix ember-deprecration-workflow

it broke because of the recent emberJS upgrade

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* log ember-data deprecations during tests

And make it cause a test failure that is forwarded to stdout.

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* findBy -> find

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* isEvery -> every

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* firstObject -> [0]

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* get(x) -> x

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* toArray(x) -> [...x]

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* mapBy -> map

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* objectAt -> []

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* addObject -> push

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* removeObject -> splice

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* fix time-zone test

Returns different results locally when TZ is not set to UTC.

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* fix test timing issues

Some attributes are now async and we need to properly wait for them to resolve.

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* update Swagger-UI SearchFilterPlugin for swagger-ui-dist v5

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* fix mfa-form test failure

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

---------

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>
Signed-off-by: Aditya <jaiswal.aditya.deelip@gmail.com>
